snippet.title: Touch Type Tale - Strategic Typing: Trailer
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/909470/

Touch Type Tale is a real-time strategy typing game in which a kingdom is thrown into turmoil and a young boy is wanted for his extraordinary gift.

Build up your economy, maneuver your troops and outsmart your opponents in multiplayer matches.
